  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl92_LabelType\">Once wronged, your vengeance can be swift and brutal.</span></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTraits_ctl00_LabelName\"><strong>Requirements</strong></span></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl92_LabelType\">Dranngvit</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl92_LabelType\">Once per day as an immediate action, you gain a +1 trait bonus on a single attack roll. In addition, if the target has damaged you within the last round, you deal 1 additional point of damage on a successful hit. You must choose to use this ability before making the attack roll.</span></p>",
